<kos/Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity/Informational> a skos:Concept ; skos:prefLabel "Informational Perceived Severity"@en .

<kos/org/agent-contact-method/Email> a skos:Concept ; skos:prefLabel "Email Contact Method"@en .
